PrecisEnactment of the CIFTA REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of customs duties paid or payable on goods that were eligible for the CANADA-ISRAEL AGREEMENT TARIFF prior to January 1, 2002, but are no longer eligible as a result of amendments to the Harmonized Commodity Description and Coding System.
